title: Mission Incomplete?

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body:
For the mission "Skill - Quick to Win" required to Win 1 game on Summoner's Rift in under 35 minutes.

Finished a game and won under 35 minutes, (34:53) why it no complete :l

replies.body: Not totally sure here, might be an issue with the last few seconds not being marked correctly.  Hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can investigate further and look into giving credit.
